~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : reboot                                    ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : reboot [<sec>/cancel]

   This will reboot the talker, either immediately or after 
   "secs" seconds.  The cancel option will cancel any timed reboot.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : shutdown
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
